      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for anyone needing a reliable, no-frills daily driver. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car starts up without issue. However, potential buyers should expect some visible wear, including minor dents and scratches on the exterior and some staining on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak running condition. Overall, it\u2019s a functional and honest car at a fair price.",
