    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin!",
